<section label="base_config" id="base_config">
<refsect1 name="Base config">
<title>BASE CONFIGURATION OPTIONS</title>
<para>The following two configuration options are in the <emphasis>base</emphasis> file:</para>

<variablelist>
  <varlistentry>
  <term>*DeskTopSize <emphasis>Columns x Rows</emphasis></term>
  <listitem>
	<para>Defines the number of view <emphasis>Columns</emphasis> by the number of view
	<emphasis>Rows</emphasis> of the desk(s) in proportional units, i.e. 2x1 would show
	2 views of one desk, one beside another.</para>

  </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
  <term>*DeskTopScale <emphasis>number</emphasis></term>
  <listitem>
	<para>If the geometry is not specified, then a desktop reduction factor is
	used to calculate the pager's size. Things in the pager window
	are shown at 1/<emphasis>number</emphasis> of the actual size.</para>

  </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</refsect1>
</section>
